### ğŸ‘¥ Interview Pattern

There were **3 rounds of interview** for GS Quant â€” all **offline** with panelists. 

All three rounds were **focused on Mathematics**, and consisted of around **5â€“6 questions** on different types of math problems and counter-questions based on your responses.

There were also questions based on what I wrote in my **resume**.  
ğŸ‘‰ So if you write any technical terms, especially related to **finance**, in your resume â€” **be sure you can explain them**.

